# resolution {{{3

DestroyMenu /Preferences/Xorg/Resolution
AddToMenu /Preferences/Xorg/Resolution
+ DynamicPopupAction MakeMenu-Resolution

DestroyFunc MakeMenu-Resolution
AddToFunc MakeMenu-Resolution
+ I DestroyMenu /Preferences/Xorg/Resolution
+ I AddToMenu /Preferences/Xorg/Resolution
+ I + DynamicPopupAction MakeMenu-Resolution
+ I Piperead 'echo "+ \\"Current: `xrandr | grep \"*\" | cut -d\' \' -f4`\\" Title"'
+ I Piperead 'xrandr | grep -v Screen | grep -v default | cut -d\' \' -f4 | while read line; do echo "+ \\"$line\\" Exec exec xrandr -s $line"; done'

