+ DynamicPopUpAction MakeMenu-Crossfade

DestroyFunc MakeMenu-Crossfade
AddToFunc MakeMenu-Crossfade
+ I DestroyMenu /Music/Crossfade
+ I AddToMenu /Music/Crossfade
+ I + DynamicPopUpAction MakeMenu-Crossfade
+ I Piperead 'echo + \"Current:\\ `mpc crossfade | sed -e \'s/^.*:\ //g\'`\" Title'
+ I + "&0"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 0
+ I + "&1"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 1
+ I + "&2"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 2
+ I + "&3"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 3
+ I + "&4"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 4
+ I + "&5"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 5
+ I + "&6"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 6
+ I + "&7"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 7
+ I + "&8"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 8
+ I + "&9"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 9
+ I + "1&0"	Exec exec mpc crossfade 10

